<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Antipalindromic_numbers">Antipalindromic numbers</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Palindromic_number&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Antipalindromic numbers"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>If the digits of a natural number don't only have to be reversed in order, but also subtracted from <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle b-1}">
